|Branches = (Parentheses denote clan suffix)<br />{{ill|Suruga Kokuzō|ja|珠流河国造|12=draft}}<br />{{ill|Kanasa clan|ja|金刺氏|12=draft}}<br />{{ill|Kuno Kokuzō|ja|久努国造|12=draft}}<br />{{ill|Kuno clan|ja|久野氏|12=draft}} (Nao)<br />{{ill|Saya clan|ja|佐夜氏|12=draft}} (Nao)<br />{{ill|Koichi Kokuzō|ja|小市国造|12=draft}}<br />{{ill|Ochi clan|ja|越智氏|12=draft}} (Nao)<br />{{ill|Kazahaya Kokuzō|ja|風速国造|12=draft}}<br />{{ill|Kazahaya clan|ja|風速氏|12=draft}} (Nao)<br />{{ill|Kuji Kokuzō|ja|久自国造|12=draft}}<br />{{ill|Ōbe clan|ja|大部氏|12=draft}} (Zō)
