: Located in {{ill|Mitsuke, Iwata|ja|磐田市見付|12=draft}}, this shrine is the {{ill|sōja|ja|惣社|12=draft}} of Tōtōmi Province and enshrines {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|12=draft}}.

