* '''{{ill|Oguni Shrine|ja|小国神社|12=draft|12=draft}}'''
: Located in {{ill|Mori, Shizuoka|ja|森町|12=draft|12=draft}}, this shrine is the {{ill|Ichinomiya|ja|一宮|12=draft|12=draft}} of Tōtōmi Province, enshrining {{ill|Ōnamuchi no Mikoto|ja|大己貴神|12=draft|12=draft}}.

