* West of the {{ill|Tenryū River|ja|天竜川|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* From Lake Hamana to the western edge of {{ill|Iwata Plain|ja|磐田原|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* From Lake Hamana to the {{ill|Ōtagawa River|ja|太田川|12=draft|12=draft}} basin.

